      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. so basically it's a toss up between growth vs concentration? is there any actual empirical evidence or recent modeling that shows which way it's actually gonna go? like, do the models show the growth usually offsets the inequality or is that just more theory?",
      "source": "evaluator"
